z = np.zeros_like(c)
for _ in range(100):
    z = z**2 + c
# Plot the result
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))
plt.imshow(np.abs(z), cmap='twilight_shifted', extent=(-2, 2, -2, 2))
plt.axis('off')
plt.title("Mandelbrot Set")
